character.name:
'VIP Client' (impeccably dressed, checking a prominent smartwatch, with an obvious look of urgency and self-importance), facing in the following cardinal directions: Front (South), Back (North), Left (West), and Right (East).

The animations should clearly convey the impatient 'power walk' (determined, slightly jerky stride, head slightly forward).
